OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774436769
OL,3,CFamily of Kent police officer killed
OL,4,Cin line of duty pay tribute
OL,6,FThe family of a Kent police officer
OL,7,Fwho died in the line of duty have paid
OL,8,Ftribute to him as "one of the finest
OL,9,Fyoung men ever to have walked this
OL,10,Fearth".
OL,12,FPolice Constable Bradley Corke, 27,
OL,13,Fdied after his response vehicle was
OL,14,Finvolved in a collision during an
OL,15,Femergency call out.
OL,17,FA second officer remains critically
OL,18,Fill in hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
