OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774436769
OL,3,CFamily of Kent police officer killed
OL,4,Cin line of duty pay tribute
OL,6,FIn a statement, PC Corke's family
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our beautiful boy, so cruelly
OL,8,Ftaken away from us far too young.
OL,10,F"Bradley was one of the finest young
OL,11,Fmen ever to have walked this earth. A
OL,12,Fcredit to himself, to us as parents
OL,13,Fand to all his family and friends who
OL,14,Floved him dearly.
OL,16,F"He was proud to be PC Bradley Corke,
OL,17,Fand in turn we are proud of his
OL,18,Fdedication to the profession.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774436769
OL,3,CFamily of Kent police officer killed
OL,4,Cin line of duty pay tribute
OL,6,FPC Corke's family added that they had
OL,7,Fbeen "touched by the outpouring of
OL,8,Flove and affection from all who knew
OL,9,Fhim".
OL,11,F"In particular, we have taken comfort
OL,12,Ffrom the kind words of those who he
OL,13,Fhelped in his line of duty, supporting
OL,14,Fthem in their hour of need," the
OL,15,Fstatement continued.
OL,17,F"It comes as no surprise to us that so
OL,18,Fmany had such a positive experience in
OL,19,Fhis presence, because that's just Brad
OL,20,F- a true gentleman in every situation
OL,21,Fhe encountered.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774436769
OL,3,CFamily of Kent police officer killed
OL,4,Cin line of duty pay tribute
OL,6,F"Son, we are broken and will probably
OL,7,Fnever recover from your loss, but we
OL,8,Fhope we can draw strength from all
OL,9,Fthat you are and forever will be.
OL,11,F"We love you son, love you with every
OL,12,Founce of our being. Sleep tight our
OL,13,Fmost beautiful boy."
OL,15,FKent Police is continuing to appeal
OL,16,Ffor anyone with information about the
OL,17,Fcollision to come forward.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
