PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774436769
OL,3,CFamily of Kent police officer killed
OL,4,Cin line of duty pay tribute
OL,6,FWitnesses or anyone with dashcam
OL,7,Ffootage should contact the Serious
OL,8,FCollision Investigation Unit on 01622
OL,9,F798538, quoting EW/AL/025/26.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe collision with PC Corke's vehicle
OL,17,Finvolved a marked Ford Focus police
OL,18,Fcar and a VW Scirocco.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
