OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774436769
OL,3,CFamily of Kent police officer killed
OL,4,Cin line of duty pay tribute
OL,6,FIt happened on the westbound A20
OL,7,FLondon Road at the junction with
OL,8,FButton Street, Farningham at
OL,9,Fapproximately 7.45pm on Thursday 19
OL,10,FMarch.
OL,12,FA member of the public who was in a
OL,13,Fsecond vehicle continues to be treated
OL,14,Ffor serious injuries.
OL,16,FOn Monday, Kent Police held a two-
OL,17,Fminute silence across the force for PC
OL,18,FCorke.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774436769
OL,3,CFamily of Kent police officer killed
OL,4,Cin line of duty pay tribute
OL,6,FA spokesperson from the force said:
OL,7,F"Bradley selflessly gave up his life
OL,8,Fwhile trying to save the lives of
OL,9,Fothers who were in danger. His
OL,10,Fbravery, dedication, and passion for
OL,11,Fhelping others will not be forgotten."
OL,13,FThey added: "He spent his police
OL,14,Fservice in the towns of West Kent. The
OL,15,Fforce is supporting his family and
OL,16,Fcolleagues, who are devastated."
OL,18,FNeil Mennie, Chair of Kent Police
OL,19,FFederation, said: "We are all
OL,20,Fabsolutely heartbroken to learn of
OL,21,Fthis news.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774436769
OL,3,CFamily of Kent police officer killed
OL,4,Cin line of duty pay tribute
OL,6,F"Bradley was a popular colleague who
OL,7,Fwill be much missed and we will be
OL,8,Fdoing all we can to support his family
OL,9,Fand close colleagues at this time.
OL,11,F"Policing is a family and words cannot
OL,12,Fdescribe the pain we are all feeling
OL,13,Fand how this news will affect us in
OL,14,Fthe days, weeks and months ahead.
OL,16,F"This sad incident serves as a
OL,17,Fhorrific example of the risks police
OL,18,Fofficers face and how police officers
OL,19,Fcan sadly make the ultimate sacrifice
OL,20,Fas they strive to keep the public
OL,21,Fsafe."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
